<span id="freeTextContainer8451111854877060459">Jenner is like a lot of us, working to pay the bills and just barely staying ahead of them. Then one day on a lark she buys a lotto ticket and much to her surprise she manages to win a super jackpot. With the new money Jenner realizes just how much her life is changing, her old friends and people either expect her to pay for things or are jealous of her. Getting sick of this she makes a change in her life. Fast forward 6 years and Jenner is living in Palm Beach and living the life of all the oth</span>
  <span id="freeText8451111854877060459" style="display:none">Jenner is like a lot of us, working to pay the bills and just barely staying ahead of them. Then one day on a lark she buys a lotto ticket and much to her surprise she manages to win a super jackpot. With the new money Jenner realizes just how much her life is changing, her old friends and people either expect her to pay for things or are jealous of her. Getting sick of this she makes a change in her life. Fast forward 6 years and Jenner is living in Palm Beach and living the life of all the other socialites that have more money than sense. It is here that she meets one of her good friends, Sydney. Sydney talks her into taking a cruise that raises money for different charities, sounds like a great girls getaway until Sydney is kidnapped and unless Jenner does what the kidnappers want Sydney will be harmed. It is here that Jenner's life takes on a slightly surreal quality and we see all sorts of crazy antics going on. <br /><br />The fun on the cruise ship becomes what is the fun of the book. Meeting all the kidnappers and the other passengers is interesting because people are rarely what they seem.</span>
